Caption:

BERLIN, GERMANY - DECEMBER 16: (L-R) Actress Katja Riemann performs together with Rene Luedicke, Anne Haug and Karim Cherif at the "Who's Afraid of Virginia Woolf" photo rehearsal at the "Theater am Kurfuerstendamm" on December 16, 2011 in Berlin, Germany. (Photo by Target Presse Agentur Gmbh/Getty Images)
